 the Producers, against which the body reacts in any case. This new investigation represents a new quality control that can be adopted to assess the safety of a vaccine. Our hypothesis is that this contamination is unintentional, since it is probably due to polluted components or procedures of industrial processes (e.g. filtrations) used to produce vaccines, not investigated and not detected by the Producers. If our hypothesis is actually the case, a close inspection of the working places and the full knowledge of the whole procedure of vaccine preparation would probably allow to eliminate the problem.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://medcraveonline.com/IJVV/IJVV-04-00072.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedcraveonline.com%2FIJVV%2FIJVV-04-00072.pdf&d=0WKnxho0shvkctxUfybzvcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=26df89f9\" target=\"_blank\">http://medcraveonline.com/IJVV/IJVV-04-00072.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n我唔信權威, 你都唔好信權威, 自已睇研究數據<br />\n<br />\n我信科學"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T12:40:08.000Z","msg":"其實點都要改善"},{"pid":"ca3270889934265e3329f1883db04ec8d38f6dc8","tid":556194,"uid":132302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T12:42:19.000Z","msg":"你就食得多重金屬食到變撚咗智障喇"},{"pid":"9c1c0be30ea3c1b69079fe863945b5987b3ad351","tid":556194,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T12:45:36.000Z","msg":"牛奶含有重金屬Ca, <br />\n<br />\n唔好飲牛奶"},{"pid":"84745f9926bb8653045c932764716877ce153e7f","tid":556194,"uid":54733,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T12:45:44.000Z","msg":"信content farm嘅人有冇讀過中學CHEM"},{"pid":"26399c9a6bc3618f98fa3c12f76f7464481de8a1","tid":556194,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T12:49:13.000Z","msg":"樓主幾時去抽走哂自己D血 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1117f207ba3b52f23c591c391b49f11eed57c0d3","tid":556194,"uid":43984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b09089febf3